&lt;p style="margin-bottom: 15px; font-style: italic;"&gt;One of the worst mistakes one can make in the face of evil is to become accustomed to it. To normalize it. No nation that aspires to prosperity can do so, and one of the expressions of evil is lying. Therefore, lies should not be tolerated, minimized, or normalized by allowing them to insult and corrupt minds with impunity.&lt;/p&gt;
